#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:4263
#, no-c-format
msgid "Samba"
msgstr "Samba"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:4264
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Samba</guilabel> is a free implementation of the <emphasis>SMB/"
"CIFS</emphasis> protocol which is used to share files and printers in a "
"network. Most modern file managers like &dolphin; and <guilabel>Nautilus</"
"guilabel> support this protocol."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Samba</guilabel> — свободная реализация протокола <emphasis>SMB/"
"CIFS</emphasis>, используемого для общего доступа к файлам и принтерам в "
"сети. Большинство современных файловых менеджеров (например, &dolphin; и "
"<guilabel>Nautilus</guilabel>) поддерживают его."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:4268
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You need to mount the share to use it in &amarok;. To do this, you need to "
"install the package <emphasis>smbfs</emphasis>. Use the command"
msgstr ""
"Для использования удалённой папки в &amarok;, её нужно примонтировать. Для "
"этого нужно установить пакет <emphasis>smbfs</emphasis> и выполнить команду"

#. Tag: userinput
#: index.docbook:4270
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"sudo mount -t cifs //<guilabel>host</guilabel>/<guilabel>share</guilabel> "
"<guilabel>/mount-point/</guilabel>"
msgstr ""
"sudo mount -t cifs //<guilabel>host</guilabel>/<guilabel>share</"
"guilabel><guilabel>/mount-point/</guilabel>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:4272
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"to mount the share. After that you can use it like a local folder and add it "
"to your local collection."
msgstr "После этого её можно использовать как локальную папку"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:4275
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>Server</title>"
msgstr "<title>Сервер</title>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:4276
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The easiest way is to use your file manager. On <guilabel>Debian</guilabel>-"
"based distributions like &ubuntu; you can install a &dolphin; extension to "
"manage shares using"
msgstr ""
"Самый простой путь — использования файлового менеджера. В дистрибутивах, "
"основанных на <guilabel>Debian</guilabel> (например, &ubuntu;) расширение "
"&dolphin; для управления удалёнными каталогами можно установить, выполнив в "
"консоли:"

#. Tag: userinput
#: index.docbook:4278
#, no-c-format
msgid "sudo apt-get install kdenetwork-filesharing"
msgstr "sudo apt-get install kdenetwork-filesharing"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:4280
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Open the properties of a folder in &dolphin; and switch to the "
"<guilabel>Share</guilabel> tab."
msgstr ""
"Откройте свойства папки в &dolphin; и выберите вкладку <guilabel>Сделать "
"общим</guilabel>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:4295
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To share the folder, just check the <guilabel>Share with Samba (Microsoft "
"Windows)</guilabel> field and set the share name under the <guilabel>Name</"
"guilabel> field. Check the <guilabel>Allow Guests</guilabel> checkbox to "
"allow anonymous users access to the folder."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:4310
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The folder should now be accessible to the network. Please see the <link "
"linkend=\"client\">Client section</link> for details on how to use it in "
"&amarok;."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:4313
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid "Universal Plug and Play (UPnP)"
msgid "Universal Plug and Play (UPnP) / DLNA"
msgstr "Universal Plug and Play (UPnP)"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:4314
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<emphasis>UPnP</emphasis> is a set of protocols to share media on the "
"network. It is also supported by a wide range of residential gateways and "
"Network Attached Storage devices. UPnP support is now commonly marketed as "
"<ulink url=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/DLNA\">DLNA</ulink>."
msgstr ""
"<emphasis>UPnP</emphasis> — набор протоколов для общего доступа к "
