"устройств. Обычно такие устройства имеют маркировку <ulink url=\"http://en."
"wikipedia.org/wiki/DLNA\">DLNA</ulink>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:4316
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "&amarok; has a build in UPnP media share client so it can play tracks "
#| "shared on the network. When a media share is discovered it will be shown "
#| "in <emphasis>Local Music</emphasis>."
msgid ""
