#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:4358
#, no-c-format
msgid "Install MySQL-Server"
msgstr "Установка сервера MySQL"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:4359
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"First you need to install an <guilabel>MySQL</guilabel> server. On Debian-"
"based distributions like Ubuntu you can use"
msgstr ""
"Сначала нужно установить сервер <guilabel>MySQL</guilabel>. В дистрибутивах, "
"основанных на Debian (например, Ubuntu), можно использовать команду:"

#. Tag: userinput
#: index.docbook:4361
#, no-c-format
msgid "sudo apt-get install mysql-server mysql-client"
msgstr "sudo apt-get install mysql-server mysql-client"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:4363
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"to install it. You will be asked to specify a password for the root-account "
"for the database. The <emphasis>mysql-client</emphasis> package is needed in "
"order to execute some of the commands in this document, but it's not "
"fundamental to the use of &amarok;."
msgstr ""
"для его установки. Нужно будет установить пароль для учётной записи "
"суперпользователя для базы данных. Для выполнения команд нужен будет пакет "
"<emphasis>mysql-client</emphasis>, но он необязателен для работы &amarok;."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:4366
#, no-c-format
msgid "Configure Database"
msgstr "Настройка базы данных"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:4367
#, no-c-format
msgid "Connect to the local database using"
msgstr "Подключитесь к локальной базе данных, выполнив:"

#. Tag: userinput
#: index.docbook:4369
#, no-c-format
msgid "mysql -u root -p"
msgstr "mysql -u root -p"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:4371
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "You will be prompted for the password for <guilabel>MySQL</"
#| "guilabel><command>'s</command> <guilabel>root</guilabel> user. You will "
#| "get the <screen>mysql&gt;</screen> prompt."
msgid ""
"You will be prompted for the password for <guilabel>MySQL's</guilabel> "
"<emphasis>root</emphasis> user. You will get the <screen>mysql&gt;</screen> "
"prompt."
msgstr ""
"Нужно будет ввести пароль для пользователя <guilabel>root</guilabel> в "
"<guilabel>MySQL</guilabel>. При успешном вводе появится строка приглашения "
"<screen>mysql&gt;</screen>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:4373
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Create a new user <replaceable>amarokuser</replaceable> with the password "
"<replaceable>amarokpass</replaceable> using the"
msgstr ""
"Создайте нового пользователя <replaceable>amarokuser</replaceable> с паролем "
"<replaceable>amarokpass</replaceable>, набрав:"

#. Tag: userinput
#: index.docbook:4375
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"CREATE USER <guilabel>'amarokuser'</guilabel>@<guilabel>'localhost'</"
"guilabel> IDENTIFIED BY <guilabel>'amarokpass'</guilabel>;"
msgstr ""
"CREATE USER <guilabel>'amarokuser'</guilabel>@<guilabel>'localhost'</"
"guilabel> IDENTIFIED BY <guilabel>'amarokpass'</guilabel>;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:4377
#, no-c-format
msgid "command. Amarok needs its own database, which is created with"
msgstr "Amarok нужна своя база данных, которую можно создать так:"

#. Tag: userinput
#: index.docbook:4379
#, no-c-format
msgid "CREATE DATABASE <guilabel>amarokdb</guilabel>;"
msgstr "CREATE DATABASE <guilabel>amarokdb</guilabel>;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:4381
#, no-c-format
msgid "Give the new user access to the database by entering the"
msgstr "Дайте новому пользователю доступ к ней:"

#. Tag: userinput
#: index.docbook:4383
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"GRANT ALL ON <guilabel>amarokdb</guilabel>.* TO <guilabel>'amarokuser'</"
"guilabel>@<guilabel>'%'</guilabel> IDENTIFIED BY <guilabel>'amarokpass'</"
"guilabel>;"
msgstr ""
"GRANT ALL ON <guilabel>amarokdb</guilabel>.* TO <guilabel>'amarokuser'</"
"guilabel>@<guilabel>'%'</guilabel> IDENTIFIED BY<guilabel>'amarokpass'</"
"guilabel>;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:4385
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"command, where <emphasis>%</emphasis> is a wildcard to allow all hosts to "
"connect to the database. Now use the"
msgstr ""
", где<emphasis>%</emphasis> — шаблон для разрешения подключения к базе "
"данных всем хостам. Теперь наберите:"

#. Tag: userinput
#: index.docbook:4387
#, no-c-format
msgid "FLUSH PRIVILEGES;"
msgstr "FLUSH PRIVILEGES;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:4389
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"statement to reload various internal caches used by <guilabel>MySQL</"
"guilabel>. Finally"
msgstr "для перезагрузки кэша <guilabel>MySQL</guilabel>. И наконец:"

#. Tag: userinput
#: index.docbook:4391
#, no-c-format
msgid "exit"
msgstr "exit"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:4393
#, no-c-format
msgid "closes the <guilabel>MySQL</guilabel> prompt."
msgstr "для выхода из командной строки <guilabel>MySQL</guilabel>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:4395
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "By default the server can only be accessed by the local host. To change "
#| "this you need to edit the file <emphasis>/etc/mysql/my.cnf</emphasis> and "
#| "adjust the address near <emphasis>bind-address</emphasis> to the one your "
#| "server listens on the network. <guilabel>0.0.0.0</guilabel> listens on "
#| "all interfaces. After that you need to restart the server using"
msgid ""
"By default the server can only be accessed by the local host. To change this "
"you need to edit the file <filename>/etc/mysql/my.cnf</filename> and adjust "
"the address near <emphasis>bind-address</emphasis> to the one your server "
"listens on the network. <guilabel>0.0.0.0</guilabel> listens on all "
"interfaces. After that you need to restart the server using"
msgstr ""
"По умолчанию, доступ к серверу разрешён только с локального компьютера. Для "
"конфигурирования этого параметра отредактируйте файл <emphasis>/etc/mysql/my."
"cnf</emphasis> и измените адрес в строке <emphasis>bind-address</emphasis> "
"на тот, который слушает ваш сервер. Используйте адрес <guilabel>0.0.0.0</"
"guilabel> для прослушивания на всех интерфейсах. После этого перезапустите "
"сервер, выполнив:"

#. Tag: userinput
#: index.docbook:4397
#, no-c-format
msgid "sudo service mysql restart"
