"смотреть клипы с YouTube."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:6768
#, no-c-format
msgid "Is it Amarok, AmaroK or amaroK?"
msgstr "Это Amarok, AmaroK или amaroK?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:6769
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "It is &amarok;! The former spelling was <emphasis>amaroK</emphasis>, but "
#| "it was changed due to its strange look."
msgid ""
"It is &amarok;! The former spelling was <emphasis>amaroK</emphasis>, but it "
"was changed due to its strange look around 2005."
msgstr ""
"Это &amarok;! Раньше он назывался <emphasis>amaroK</emphasis>, но, из-за "
"странного вида, мы поменяли название."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:6772
#, no-c-format
msgid "How are track scores determined?"
msgstr "Как определяется рейтинг для дорожки?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:6773
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&amarok; assigns a score (a number 0-100) to a song based on how many times "
"you've listened to it and whether you skip the song without it finishing. "
"Every time the song finishes playing, the score is changed."
msgstr ""
"&amarok; присваивает дорожке число (0-100) на основании того, как много раз "
"вы её слушали и сколько раз промотали. После прослушивания дорожки, её "
"рейтинг меняется."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:6775
#, no-c-format
msgid "Here you have an example script that can calculate scores:"
msgstr "Вот простой сценарий для подсчёта рейтинга:"

#. Tag: screen
#: index.docbook:6777
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"if( playcount &lt;= 0 ) # not supposed to be less, but what the hell.\n"
"       newscore = ( prevscore + percentage ) / 2\n"
"   else\n"
"       newscore = ( ( prevscore * playcount ) + percentage ) / ( playcount + "
"1 )\n"
"   end"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:6779
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "You can easily create your own script with your own algorithm. Look at "
#| "the <ulink url=\"http://amarok.kde.org/wiki/Development/"
#| "Scripting_HowTo_2.0\">Script-Writing-Howto</ulink> for further "
#| "information."
msgid ""
"You can easily create your own script with your own algorithm. Look at the "
"<ulink url=\"http://community.kde.org/Amarok/Development/"
"Scripting_HowTo_2.0\">Script-Writing-Howto</ulink> for further information."
msgstr ""
"Вы можете легко написать свой сценарий, со своим алгоритмом. Посмотрите вот "
"<ulink url=\"http://amarok.kde.org/wiki/Development/Scripting_HowTo_2.0\"> "
"это</ulink>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:6782
#, no-c-format
msgid "How do I manually change a track's score?"
msgstr "Как поменять рейтинг дорожки вручную?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:6783
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "You may change the score manually in the <emphasis>Edit Track Details</"
#| "emphasis> dialog, available by right-clicking on a track, and choosing "
#| "the <guilabel>Summary</guilabel> tab. Before &amarok; 2.4.1, this is "
#| "called the <guilabel>Statistics</guilabel> tab."
msgid ""
"You may change the score manually in the <guilabel>Track Details</guilabel> "
"dialog, available by right-clicking on a track, choosing <guilabel>Edit "
"Track Details</guilabel> and going to the <guilabel>Summary</guilabel> tab."
msgstr ""
"Вы можете поменять рейтинг дорожки во вкладке <guilabel>Сводка</guilabel> "
"(до &amarok; 2.4.1 <guilabel>Статистика</guilabel>) окна <emphasis>Сведения "
"о дорожке</emphasis>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:6786
#, no-c-format
msgid "But I also want that stars system like in other players!"
msgstr ""
"Но пятизвёздочная система рейтинга, как в других плеерах, мне тоже нравится!"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:6787
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "&amarok;, of course, supports an user-defined rating system, and you can "
#| "rate your tracks with a single click using the <emphasis>Current Track "
